section.div: Dify is an open-source LLM app development platform. Dify's intuitive interface combines AI workflow, RAG pipeline, agent capabilities, model management, observability features and more, letting you quickly go from prototype to production.

LeetSync is a Chrome extension that enables you to sync your LeetCode problem submissions with a selected GitHub repository. With this extension, you can easily track your coding progress and share your solutions with others on GitHub.
